{"data":[{"name":"88:1","price":"（使徒*よ、）圧倒的事態¹の話は、あなたに届いたか？","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡغَٰشِيَةِ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5968,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「圧倒的事態」とは、その恐怖で人々を圧倒する、復活の日*のこと（ムヤッサル５９２頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"hal atāka ḥadīthu al-ghāshiyati ","translations":["Has","(there) come to you","(the) news","(of) the Overwhelming","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["hal","atāka","ḥadīthu","al-ghāshiyati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1200],[3,1200,2050],[4,2050,3925]]}},{"name":"88:2","price":"その日、（不信仰者*たちの）顔は、（懲罰への）恐怖に陥っている。","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ خَٰشِعَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5969,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wujūhun yawma-idhin khāshiʿatun ","translations":["Faces","that Day","(will be) humbled","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wujūhun","yawma-idhin","khāshiʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,3160],[3,3160,4965]]}},{"name":"88:3","price":"（それらの顔は、過酷な）労役に就き、消耗している。","arabic":"عَامِلَةٞ نَّاصِبَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5970,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿāmilatun nāṣibatun ","translations":["Laboring","exhausted","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿāmilatun","nāṣibatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1210],[2,1210,3985]]}},{"name":"88:4","price":"（それらは、）酷熱の業火に入って炙られる。","arabic":"تَصۡلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5971,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"taṣlā nāran ḥāmiyatan ","translations":["They will burn","(in) a Fire","intensely hot","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["taṣlā","nāran","ḥāmiyatan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1630],[3,1630,3355]]}},{"name":"88:5","price":"（それらは、）煮えたぎる泉から、飲まされる。¹","arabic":"تُسۡقَىٰ مِنۡ عَيۡنٍ ءَانِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5972,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　地獄の民の飲食物については、洞窟章２９、イブラーヒーム*章１６－１７、整列者章６２－６６、サード章５７－５８、煙霧章４３－４６、ムハンマド*章１５、出来事章５２－５５、衣を纏（まと）う 者章１３、真実章３６－３７なども参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"tus'qā min ʿaynin āniyatin ","translations":["They will be given to drink","from","a spring","boiling","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["tus'qā","min","ʿaynin","āniyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1090],[3,1090,2070],[4,2070,3715]]}},{"name":"88:6","price":"彼らには、忌々しい植物¹しか、食べ物がない。","arabic":"لَّيۡسَ لَهُمۡ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5973,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「忌々しい植物」の解釈には、「炎の木」「ザックーム（夜の旅章６０「呪われた木」の訳注を参照）」「棘のある植物の一種」といった諸説がある（イブン・カスィール８：３８５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"laysa lahum ṭaʿāmun illā min ḍarīʿin ","translations":["Not is","for them","food","except","from","a bitter thorny plant","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["laysa","lahum","ṭaʿāmun","illā","min","ḍarīʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1200],[3,1200,2250],[4,2250,3180],[5,3180,4510],[6,4510,7285]]}},{"name":"88:7","price":"（それらは彼らを）太らせもしなければ、（彼らの）飢えを満たしてもくれない。","arabic":"لَّا يُسۡمِنُ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِن جُوعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5974,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yus'minu walā yugh'nī min jūʿin ","translations":["Not","it nourishes","and not","it avails","from","hunger","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yus'minu","walā","yugh'nī","min","jūʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,440],[2,440,1330],[3,1330,1860],[4,1860,2750],[5,2750,3090],[6,3090,6355]]}},{"name":"88:8","price":"（復活の）その日、（信仰者たちの）顔は、恩恵を享受している。","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاعِمَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5975,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wujūhun yawma-idhin nāʿimatun ","translations":["Faces","that Day","(will be) joyful","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wujūhun","yawma-idhin","nāʿimatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,2430],[3,2430,5635]]}},{"name":"88:9","price":"（それらは、）自分たちの（現世で行った）努力（への褒美）ゆえに満足している、","arabic":"لِّسَعۡيِهَا رَاضِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5976,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lisaʿyihā rāḍiyatun ","translations":["With their effort","satisfied","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["lisaʿyihā","rāḍiyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,2965]]}},{"name":"88:10","price":"高き楽園の中で。","arabic":"فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5977,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fī jannatin ʿāliyatin ","translations":["In","a garden","elevated","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","jannatin","ʿāliyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2200],[3,2200,3725]]}},{"name":"88:11","price":"（それらは、）そこで戯言¹を耳にすることもない。","arabic":"لَّا تَسۡمَعُ فِيهَا لَٰغِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5978,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「戯言については、信仰者たち章３の同語の訳注を参照（アッ＝サアディー９２１頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lā tasmaʿu fīhā lāghiyatan ","translations":["Not","they will hear","therein","vain talk","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","tasmaʿu","fīhā","lāghiyatan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,1330],[3,1330,2280],[4,2280,3975]]}},{"name":"88:12","price":"そこには、流れる泉がある。","arabic":"فِيهَا عَيۡنٞ جَارِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5979,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhā ʿaynun jāriyatun ","translations":["Therein","(will be) a spring","flowing","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhā","ʿaynun","jāriyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,810],[2,810,2400],[3,2400,4174]]}},{"name":"88:13","price":"そこには、高い寝台がある。","arabic":"فِيهَا سُرُرٞ مَّرۡفُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5980,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhā sururun marfūʿatun ","translations":["Therein","(will be) thrones","raised high","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhā","sururun","marfūʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1540],[3,1540,4315]]}},{"name":"88:14","price":"また、配置された杯、","arabic":"وَأَكۡوَابٞ مَّوۡضُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5981,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-akwābun mawḍūʿatun ","translations":["And cups","put in place","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-akwābun","mawḍūʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,4005]]}},{"name":"88:15","price":"並べられた肘掛け、","arabic":"وَنَمَارِقُ مَصۡفُوفَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5982,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wanamāriqu maṣfūfatun ","translations":["And cushions","lined up","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["wanamāriqu","maṣfūfatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,3005]]}},{"name":"88:16","price":"敷き広げられた絨毯がある。","arabic":"وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبۡثُوثَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5983,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wazarābiyyu mabthūthatun ","translations":["And carpets","spread out","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["wazarābiyyu","mabthūthatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1530],[2,1530,3475]]}},{"name":"88:17","price":"一体、彼ら（不信仰者*たち）は、ラクダがいかに創られたのか、見て（考え）ないのか？","arabic":"أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡإِبِلِ كَيۡفَ خُلِقَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5984,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"afalā yanẓurūna ilā al-ibili kayfa khuliqat ","translations":["Then do not","they look","towards","the camels","how","they are created","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["afalā","yanẓurūna","ilā","al-ibili","kayfa","khuliqat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,2740],[3,2740,3130],[4,3130,4050],[5,4050,4670],[6,4670,5995]]}},{"name":"88:18","price":"また天が、いかに上げられたのかを？","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5985,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-samāi kayfa rufiʿat ","translations":["And towards","the sky","how","it is raised","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-samāi","kayfa","rufiʿat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,3240],[3,3240,3810],[4,3810,5175]]}},{"name":"88:19","price":"また、山々がいかに据え付けられたのかを？","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5986,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-jibāli kayfa nuṣibat ","translations":["And towards","the mountains","how","they are fixed","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-jibāli","kayfa","nuṣibat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1720],[3,1720,2330],[4,2330,3585]]}},{"name":"88:20","price":"また、大地がいかに平坦に伸ばされたかを？","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَيۡفَ سُطِحَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5987,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-arḍi kayfa suṭiḥat ","translations":["And towards","the earth","how","it is spread out","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-arḍi","kayfa","suṭiḥat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1530],[3,1530,2070],[4,2070,3375]]}},{"name":"88:21","price":"ならば（使徒*よ、人々に、啓示で）教訓を与えよ。あなたは教訓を与える者でしかないのだから。","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5988,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhakkir innamā anta mudhakkirun ","translations":["So remind","only","you","(are) a reminder","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhakkir","innamā","anta","mudhakkirun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,4020],[3,4020,5240],[4,5240,6615]]}},{"name":"88:22","price":"あなたは、彼らに対（して信仰へと無理強い）する制圧者などではない。","arabic":"لَّسۡتَ عَلَيۡهِم بِمُصَيۡطِرٍ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5989,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lasta ʿalayhim bimuṣayṭirin ","translations":["You are not","over them","a controller","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["lasta","ʿalayhim","bimuṣayṭirin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,2310],[3,2310,3945]]}},{"name":"88:23","price":"但し、（教訓に）背を向け、不信仰（の固執）に陥った者は別で、","arabic":"إِلَّا مَن تَوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5990,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"illā man tawallā wakafara ","translations":["But","whoever","turns away","and disbelieves","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","man","tawallā","wakafara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1890],[3,1890,3020],[4,3020,4295]]}},{"name":"88:24","price":"アッラー*は彼を（、業火という）最大の懲罰で罰される。","arabic":"فَيُعَذِّبُهُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلۡعَذَابَ ٱلۡأَكۡبَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5991,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fayuʿadhibuhu al-lahu al-ʿadhāba al-akbara ","translations":["Then will punish him","Allah","(with) the punishment","greatest","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["fayuʿadhibuhu","al-lahu","al-ʿadhāba","al-akbara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1450],[2,1450,2280],[3,2280,3350],[4,3350,4975]]}},{"name":"88:25","price":"本当にわれら*にこそ、彼らの（死後の）帰り所があるのだから。","arabic":"إِنَّ إِلَيۡنَآ إِيَابَهُمۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5992,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ilaynā iyābahum ","translations":["Indeed","to Us","(will be) their return","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ilaynā","iyābahum",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1380],[2,1380,3820],[3,3820,5625]]}},{"name":"88:26","price":"それから、本当にわれら*にこそ、彼らの（行いの）清算が委ねられているのだから。","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا حِسَابَهُم","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5993,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma inna ʿalaynā ḥisābahum ","translations":["Then","indeed","upon Us","(is) their account","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","inna","ʿalaynā","ḥisābahum",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1320],[2,1320,2750],[3,2750,3910],[4,3910,7165]]}}],"chapter":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah","Chapter Al-Ghashiyah","Ghashiyah","Surah Ghashiyah","Chapter Ghashiyah","Al Ghashiyah","Surah Al Ghashiyah","Chapter Al Ghashiyah","Surah 88","Chapter 88","The Overwhelming Event","الغاشية"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}